                ],
                "institute": "3AULAUA"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The 3 MV Van De Graff Accelerator"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A set of standards was prepared by conventionally",
                "implanting silicon wafers with 50-keV 14-N+ ions at",
                "a dose of 5.6E+13 ions/cm2 using the implantation",
                "facilities.",
                "Samples of a high alloy proprietary steel marketed as",
                "Viking (0.5%-C,1.0%-Si,0.5%-Mn,8.0%-Cr,1.5%-Mo and",
                "0.5%-V) were tempered at 540 degree and treated by",
                "plasma immersion ion implantation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The cross sections obtained in this work were used for",
                "measuring the nitrogen depth profile in Viking tool",
                "steel."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 50 mm*2 silicon surface barrier detector",
                "of 1 mm thickness was placed at 5.8 mm from the beam",
                "spot on the sample. A slit of 2 mm width and 8 mm",
                "height was placed in front of the detector in order to",
                "definite the reaction angle."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "STATUS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "status": [
                  "TABLE"
                ],
                "subentry_number": null,
                "author": null,
